Package: hstone
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve and analyze Hearthstone cards and decks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nam Hee", "Kim", email = "nhk2120@columbia.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: You can obtain various useful information that will help you in Hearth Stone. 
   Get information on all the Hearthstone cards with your choice of card classification and analyze the deck with deck codes.
   You can get the average mana cost for the cards and the deck you searched. You can also expect the type of deck.
   In addition, it is extremely easy to get top tier deckcodes by running a simple function and retrieve the most used cards from the top tier decks.
